  "title": "Recruitment Consultant",
  "description": "<p>What does a Recruitment Consultant do? </p><ul><li><p>Proactively interact and maintain great relationships with top companies in the Asia Pacific regions which extends to our global network </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>You will act as a professional consultant who can understand the client's needs in terms of executive talent </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>You will act as an advisor to help top candidates find their Dream job </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>You will help companies solve their Number 1 challenge: Talents </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>You will be equipped with technical knowledge and be updated with current market conditions and be aware of organizations that are looking to hire mid to senior level executives with the big support of experienced mentors & leaders internally </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Working efficiently and effectively on daily basis in order to become financially independent and successful! </p></li></ul><p>Our consultants are of diverse backgrounds, but they are ALL: </p><ul><li><p>Highly ambitious and highly competitive </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Enjoys ales and achieving goals </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Very sociable people who love to create relationships </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Have the ability to learn fast and continuously improve </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Have a great attitude and strong work ethnics </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Have strong leadership qualities </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Fluent in English </p></li></ul><p>What are the perks of being a Recruitment Consultant? </p><ul><li><p>Unlimited career progression without any time limit in a meritocratic environment </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Opportunity to work with Exceptional Senior Management and passionate and driven Team </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Transparent progression scheme with 100% potential in earning uncapped monthly commissions </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>The ability to work or relocate to our 12 awesome global locations </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Exceptional and Engaging recruitment training from basic to experienced academy  </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>A young, fun and entrepreneurial environment with an amazing office location in CBD </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Medical Insurance coverage for you and your family </p></li></ul>",
